summary: This preset can be added to RaceMenu
descriptionHtml:
This preset can be added to RaceMenu. Feel free to submit pictures of any kind. Nude, Clothed, armoured. Whatever you wish. I will credit you. If the preset doesn't work (doesn't look like it is on the pictures), you might need this mod: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70834/]Demoniac- High Quality Glossy Female Body Texture 8K 4K 2K[/url]﻿.

Please check requirements!!!
